## رسالة 3: نسخة إنجليزية (لجروبات إنجليزي)

```
Assalamu Alaikum 👋

🕌 We're building "Salati" — an open-source Windows desktop app for prayer time reminders.

What it does:
• Runs in background (System Tray)
• Alerts before prayer with Adhan sound
• Auto prayer times via API or manual input
• Arabic + English + Dark/Light theme

Tech Stack:
• C# — .NET 9 — WinForms + Guna.UI2
• SQL Server + T-SQL + Stored Procedures
• 3-Tier Architecture (DAL → BLL → UI)

Current status:
✅ 9 screens designed
✅ 8 database tables planned
✅ Full documentation ready
✅ Ready to start coding

Looking for:
🔧 Backend devs (C#)
🎨 UI devs (WinForms)
🗄 DB devs (SQL Server)
🧪 Testers

All levels welcome! 🤝

Join us 👇
https://t.me/+vcAJ88vJKjI5MmM0
```
